    <!-- About us -->

    <section id="about-us">
        <div class="heading-container">
            <div class="geeks">
                <h1 class="index-heading">about us</h1>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container-fluid  d-flex justify-content-center mt-5">
            <div class=" col-3 card m-3 about-us-cards jiggle">
                <img src="/public/Images/Home/About Us Cards/Sitting.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="card-text">
                        Best of its class, well designed, peaceful and fully air conditioned infrastructure.
                        Personal Cabins with Charging Ports along with clean, hygienic washrooms and filtered frinking
                        water. Personal Locker Rooms. Wifi Connectivity with 24*7 Power Supply and Backups Generator
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class=" col-3 card m-3 about-us-cards jiggle">
                <img src="/public/Images/Home/About Us Cards/Magzine Rack.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="card-text">For those how wants to keep themselves up to date, we provide you an archive
                        filled with leading Newspaper and Magzines in both English and Hindi.
                    <ul>

                        <li>
                            Newspapers
                            <ul>
                                <li>Dainik Bhaskar</li>
                                <li>Hindustan Times</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>Magzines
                            <ul>
                                <li>India Today</li>
                                <li>Forbes India</li>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    And much more......
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class=" col-3 card m-3 about-us-cards jiggle">
                <img src="/public/Images/Home/About Us Cards/Book Issue.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="card-text">We keep customer satisfaction at our top priority. Reading in not only to be
                        done in here, take books to you with home. We keep our selves updated and refresh our collection
                        on quaterly basis.</p>
                    <p>You can make a request to us for the resources that not available in our collection, we will try
                        our best to provide you with that.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class=" col-3 card m-3 about-us-cards jiggle">
                <img src="/public/Images/Home/About Us Cards/Sanitization.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="card-text">Covid-19 is no new news to anyone. Inspite of that, our daily life cannot be
                        stopped and to make your study time safe. Here we follow all guidelines instructed by the
                        government. From all basic rules of Mask-on and social distancing to every day sanitization of
                        the facilty we are all prepared to fight this Virus.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>




